text: Telemundo is a Turkish pay television owned by NBCUniversal International Networks. The channel is available on DigiTurk. The channel launched on 15 September 1994. The channel aired shows from the US Telemundo dubbed in Turkish. However, the channel was replaced by NBC that was launched on 17 July 2008. It was later revived on 23 June 2024 as a replacement of Syfy. Category:Telemundo Category:Television channels in Europe
title: Telemundo (Turkish TV channel)
